channel.title: Back in the game
channel.description: Hey mopar community. I doubt anyone here knows me, but i'd say by now I would be considered RSPS veteran(just check my registration date :P). I don't use this name anymore, i now go by SeeSaw. Why am i back? I recently moved because of school so i needed a new hobby, so i thought why not bring back an old one. I was introduced to RSPS's from Dodian, and am back because i have recently made a remake of it. So far, its very popular with 600+ votes in a month so im definintely here to stay and work on my server for fun. I am a marketing major, so i wouldn't call myself a programmer, but i enjoy a little coding. I noticed mopar is no longer the top dog of rsps's, but it was in my day so i'll be on here every now and then. Not much else to say besides that it's a pleasure to be back!
